data.description: Discover the epitome of comfortable living in this charming brick two owner one and a half story custom built home nestled in The Oaks subdivision. On the main level you will find everything you need from the beautiful Master Bedroom, private office, open family room with a gas fireplace, formal dining room, kitchen and utility room. As you enter upstairs you will find ample space. Three bedrooms, one full bathroom . The finished walkout basement offers unlimited possibilities. One bedroom, one full bath, two bonus rooms, bar area and tons of storage.This home has been well cared for.New roof in 2021, HVAC 2021, Interior paint 2023, exterior paint front door and garage 2023, Hardwood floors refinished 2024, New Carpet being installed in the master bedroom, Living Room and stairs leading to the basement. Kitchen cabinets refinished, Invisible dog fence installed 2022. Just to list a few items see sellers disclosure for full list. Buyers to verify all aspects of the home including square footage.
